# G rename

Rename a field across model, DTOs, service, tests; emit a rename
migration. Preview by default.

1. Ask the user for `<Resource>.<OldField> <NewField>`.
2. Run `gofasta g rename <args> --json` (preview mode).
3. Show every file the generator would patch and the migration pair
   it would emit.
4. Only re-run with `--apply` after the user confirms.
